## Execution Protocol

1. Select the target Design Doc.
2. If the user wants generated test skeletons first, invoke `dev-workflows-dotnet:acceptance-test-generator`.
3. Invoke `dev-workflows-dotnet:work-planner` with the Design Doc and any generated integration/E2E skeleton paths.
4. Present the resulting work plan for approval and revise if needed.
